Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:41.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,把頭抬起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:44.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:46.57,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我叫井兒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.94,0:01:48.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井兒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:55.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,果真 這個真的是你做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:56.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.25,0:02:05.29,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,因為出生在窯爐裏得到窯的正氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:07.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,沒想到會是如此境界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:21.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,爹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:28.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,爹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:42.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,李江天 柳乙檀你們兩位邊首要奉御令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:46.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,在分院郎廳競賽裏要全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:49.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,微臣接旨 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:54.84,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,競賽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:58.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不是分明說好由李邊首就任嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:02:59.98,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,為何還要競賽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:02.18,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:04.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,競賽只不過是形式而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:09.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,柳乙檀他的器具 根本與宮裏不相配
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:12.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你還真是太平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.45,0:03:16.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,在這個朝鮮 最為貴重而寶貴的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:18.69,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不就是王室白瓷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:23.83,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,分院郎廳即是管理王室瓷器的\N最高頭領之位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.83,0:03:27.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這個財路 要由我們來掌握啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:31.54,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那個位置一定要由我們的人來坐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.91,0:03:33.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:35.21,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 娘娘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:37.41,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,去見李邊首吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:46.22,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,李邊首
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.59,0:03:52.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,天下無敵李邊首的自尊心\N看來傷得不輕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:56.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,乙檀是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:04:02.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,他只是製作膚淺的器具的市井之徒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.37,0:04:05.31,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我一定要坐上分院郎廳位置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:11.18,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,洗掉今日的恥辱 提高王室瓷器品格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:13.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,理應如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:19.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可是我說啊 也要做好最壞的打算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.99,0:04:23.66,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您不相信微臣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:25.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:29.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我只是不相信殿下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:35.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:38.71,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,為何只有你們幾個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:42.38,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是還未通知其他陶瓷匠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:44.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:49.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要做出吸引殿下之心的最好的器具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:51.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,希望你們能配合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:56.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,都去了李邊首的工坊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:05:01.46,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那更要抓緊時間\N為何連煉土工作也沒有做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:03.67,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那個也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:04.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:08.07,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人善用的鳳山白土
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:11.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,李邊首大人他們都給拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.11,0:05:13.21,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:19.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,他覺得梅花圖會不穩定\N李邊首不使用鳳山白土
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:20.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,所以說啊 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:23.12,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,分明就是在這次競賽裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:26.05,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,想要陷大人於困境的意圖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:30.46,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,剩下的白土就只有宣川白土嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:32.29,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是的 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:37.07,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:41.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我正想試用宣川白土會如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:43.31,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,萬萬不可啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.31,0:05:45.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要是平常還好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:49.18,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,放著朗廳之位競爭的重要時期\N怎麼能試用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不是還有蓮玉你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:54.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你幫李邊首數年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:57.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你應該很瞭解他所使用的宣川白土
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:06:00.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,趁此機會 你就盡情展示你的實力吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:02.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:04.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,來 我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:07.16,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.60,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,福到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:18.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,每個人都充滿福氣 充滿福氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:21.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,給你 你也受到福氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:25.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,給你 受福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:23.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,果然你的瓷器是充滿樸實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:24.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:30.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如此精細而華麗的瓷器\N沒人能比得上你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:37.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你這是表示有自信嗎\N看你今日氣色不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:40.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我做了一個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:44.79,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,看起來像我女兒的 漂亮的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:48.10,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,居然會獻給殿下白瓷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:52.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,做的什麼白日夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:55.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你都這把年齡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:58.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,別說是女兒 都還沒娶妻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:00.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:18.93,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,青鹽的白色 穿著華麗的櫻花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:21.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,寡人接觸過數多王室的瓷器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:25.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,無論色感 形態 觸感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:28.84,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如此深得我心的茶杯 好久沒遇到過了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:31.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是李邊首的手藝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:35.08,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,讓您見笑了 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:39.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,覺得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:41.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是的 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:46.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,與大王的威嚴相配的\N果真是威儀的茶杯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:51.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,王室所用的瓷器就由李邊首負責吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:53.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:08:59.67,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎麼會如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:04.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如此鮮明的指痕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:19.12,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下 容臣妾說一句嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:21.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,請講
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:25.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,驀然一看 是很粗糙\N可越看越會覺得舒適
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:28.66,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我想把那茶杯 佔為己有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:33.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,確實是很粗燥的瓷器 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:39.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,寡人也會被它那奇妙的灑脫感所吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:41.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,柳邊首
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:43.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:48.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,日後寡人的專用瓷器就由你負責吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.22,0:09:52.15,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,謝主隆恩 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:56.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下 王室專屬瓷器是李邊首
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:58.76,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下專用瓷器是柳邊首
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:10:01.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這競賽的結果是如何決定的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:05.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,分院朗廳只會是一個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:08.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,二人中只選其一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:09.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:14.18,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,茶杯的優劣不是看賣相而是看功用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:16.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不如以品茶定勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:22.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這杯茶就由恭嬪你來品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:25.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:51.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,娘娘...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:53.08,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,娘娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:57.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,謀 謀反
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:11:00.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,有人要謀害寡人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.42,0:11:05.93,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,來人 內禁衛 內禁衛護駕 內禁衛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:08.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,保護殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:12.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:25.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這是不是你用的釉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:38.59,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:47.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,燒廚房和內醫院都沒發現毒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:52.17,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,唯一值得懷疑之物就是茶杯上的釉粉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:54.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,還不從實招來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:12:00.62,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,絕不寬饒 寡人絕不會寬饒你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:03.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,用了什麼毒 是砒霜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:12.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下\N微臣製作的釉中絕沒摻雜任何毒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:14.56,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,請相信微臣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:15.66,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,混賬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:20.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,恭嬪都倒下了\N你卻謊稱無毒 還要我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:24.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,來人 把他拉出去斬首
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:25.21,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:30.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不 此事不能就這麼算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:35.12,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,一介沙器匠\N絕不可能犯下此等滔天大案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:38.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是誰 誰是主謀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:39.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是誰指使你幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:42.46,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,微臣冤枉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:46.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如果喝光這些釉就可證明微臣的清白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:49.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,微臣甘之若貽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:12:59.71,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:03.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下 不是毒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:08.15,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那不是中毒 是蕁麻疹 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:10.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,蕁麻疹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:14.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,恭嬪娘娘患有桃花蕁麻疹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:21.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,輕則會有搔癢癥狀\N重則會氣血堵塞造成昏厥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:25.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,萬幸娘娘已恢復了神智 正在靜養中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:35.31,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,混賬 你在釉中加入了桃花嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:54.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這都怪微臣失察
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:56.23,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,此人意圖謀害娘娘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:58.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,恭請殿下治他謀逆之罪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:01.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,治他謀逆之罪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:06.88,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,為什麼要在釉中加入桃花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:10.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,莫非你早就知道恭嬪患有桃花蕁麻疹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:13.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下 微臣一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:18.62,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,釉中加入桃花是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:20.46,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:23.76,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:26.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,一介沙器匠不可能知道娘娘的病癥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:31.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,微臣與柳邊首共事多年\N他絕不是謀逆之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:34.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,請您明察
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:36.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不是謀逆之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:44.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,既不是故意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.68,0:14:48.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,雖危機嬪妃之命 也就證明沒有罪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:52.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你是這個意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.96,0:14:57.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,微臣惶恐 殿下 微臣只是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:14:59.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,寡人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:03.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,看錯你了 李邊首
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:21.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,卿你怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:25.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,雖然李邊首有點僭越
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:28.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,寡人還以為他是個只知道制陶的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.46,0:15:31.66,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,沒想到他還很有眼色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:36.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這種氣量分院交給他管理又有何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:42.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下真的這麼說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:44.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:49.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,事情能這麼圓滿解決\N真是有如神助啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:51.48,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:56.62,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,恭嬪的蕁麻疹您是怎麼得知的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:59.56,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,賞花時偶然得知
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:03.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,健康時自不足慮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,0:16:08.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不過以現在快臨產的虛弱身子骨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:18.64,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,任命李江天為分院郎廳\N務必盡心盡責
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:22.31,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,恭喜您 朗廳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:24.15,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,恭喜您
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:26.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,郎廳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:29.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小的有事相問
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:32.22,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,真的是因為釉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:35.16,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,柳邊首大人會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:38.83,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,朗廳大人 朗廳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:41.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,都說不行的了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.13,0:16:45.07,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就一會兒 見個面就回
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:46.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,求您了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:49.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:53.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:16:58.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:03.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你怎麼進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:07.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,都怪我 大人才會受這種苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:10.76,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:12.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,因為我製作的釉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:18.83,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下命我 製作御用茶器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:25.81,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你和我一起製作的茶器 越看越愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:28.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,越看越吸引人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.85,0:17:30.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:35.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我害怕不能告訴你這些話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.19,0:17:39.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,總算了卻了心事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:44.16,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我之所以要成為分院朗廳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.26,0:17:47.83,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是因為惜你之才
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:52.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,沙器匠之位不是一個女子可以僭越的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:56.64,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,明知道這一點卻不放棄夢想的你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:01.41,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是那麼的美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.71,0:18:11.69,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,製作敬獻給殿下的器物中\N膽敢摻入私心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.05,0:18:15.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,稱我為謀逆之徒也不為過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:19.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你要在李朗廳手下苦練技藝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:25.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,登上分院沙器匠之位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.47,0:18:31.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你一定要成為朝鮮第一位女沙器匠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:37.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不管我身在何處 即便
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:41.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不在此世
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.62,0:18:48.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,也會為你祈福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:50.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:16.29,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這麼醜的茶杯\N竟然能入得了你的法眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:20.69,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下的眼光真是無人能及
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:25.83,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如果不是仁嬪娘娘 結果將完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:33.54,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,總而言之\N最後成為分院朗廳之人可是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:44.18,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,與乙坦的恩怨就此勾銷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:46.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,擔心乙坦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:48.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,還不如擔心怎麼治理分院
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.69,0:19:53.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不能再因此事引起任何風波
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:57.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我說的話 希望你銘記於心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.90,0:20:04.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,朗廳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:18.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您為什麼會送我桃花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:24.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,桃花可提高釉的黏度\N使之輕易黏附於器物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.29,0:20:28.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可配宣川白土的釉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.96,0:20:30.79,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,別忘了是你自己找我來向我求救的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:35.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,收回其他白土 也是因為這個目的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:40.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,為了利用我製作可陷害乙憛大人的釉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.44,0:20:42.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你可不能亂說話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:46.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這一切我要向義禁府告發
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:50.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,命我在釉中加入桃花之人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:54.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,正是郎廳大人您 就這麼告發
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.46,0:21:07.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你敢謊報事實
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:13.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,使用鬼蜮伎倆的是朗廳大人您
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:22.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你心中不是懷有成為沙器匠的\N大志的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:28.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不要因小失大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:33.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,沙器匠之位我可...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.92,0:21:36.12,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,為了成為沙器匠的夢想\N我堅忍到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:39.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,被大人蹂躪的那一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:46.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,也沒有自絕堅忍到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:47.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:50.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我終於明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.17,0:21:52.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.01,0:21:59.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,沒有比柳邊首大人更可貴的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:03.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,難道...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.75,0:22:08.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你對他...對乙檀那人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:11.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,愛慕著他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.09,0:22:16.50,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我豈敢喜歡柳邊首大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.23,0:22:20.54,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我沒有那資格 您應該比我更清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.74,0:22:26.04,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,若你敢說出釉的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.14,0:22:31.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你的性命 恐怕也保不住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.38,0:22:35.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就算拼上性命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.32,0:22:39.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,也要救柳邊首大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.36,0:22:43.66,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,等天一亮 我就去義禁府
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.90,0:22:52.10,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就連你這不起眼的女人也
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.84,0:22:56.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,乙檀 乙檀 乙檀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.88,0:23:09.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,馬風
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.29,0:24:22.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.86,0:24:25.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.69,0:24:27.16,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我懷孕了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.16,0:24:29.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,陣痛已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.47,0:24:35.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我腹中的孩子是誰的\N你也很清楚不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.44,0:24:41.84,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你怎麼敢殺害你主人的血脈呀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.58,0:24:48.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,回去轉告他\N這個孩子的胎夢是窯爐的大吉之夢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.45,0:24:49.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,回去轉告他
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.93,0:25:02.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.50,0:25:05.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,懷孕了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.74,0:25:12.31,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,窯爐的吉夢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.31,0:25:15.98,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,他說絕對不能有弟弟妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.55,0:25:20.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不可以笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.75,0:25:28.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如果有弟弟妹妹\N就會被搶走所有的富貴權勢和名譽
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.09,0:25:30.29,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,分明是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.39,0:25:33.23,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.73,0:25:42.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,毓道 怎麼還沒有睡呀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.77,0:25:46.81,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,為了祝賀您 等著等著 剛才睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.18,0:25:49.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,幸好聽到大門的聲音 醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.48,0:25:53.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,夜很深了 怎麼不直接睡覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.42,0:25:56.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎麼能等到天亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.35,0:26:03.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,父親成為分院郎廳的事情\N真是讓我高興和自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.06,0:26:11.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,兒子也會努力成為能繼承父親的\N朝鮮第一的沙器匠的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.24,0:26:20.21,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,當然 快回去睡吧 毓道
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.21,0:26:22.04,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 父親
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.35,0:26:30.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我的血脈毓道一個就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.68,0:27:03.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,來 看看看看
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.80,0:27:15.63,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,辛苦了 恭嬪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.87,0:27:25.17,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,今天是好日子 除了重罪犯人之外
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.17,0:27:27.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,赦免釋放牢裏所有的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.89,0:27:49.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,罪人 柳乙檀 免去邊首一職\N從分院逐放
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.28,0:29:18.22,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,蓮玉 你不是蓮玉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.06,0:29:21.16,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.62,0:29:25.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 你怎麼在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.19,0:29:27.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎麼會在這樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.23,0:29:30.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.07,0:29:32.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這孩子是...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.00,0:29:38.41,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這不是做夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.88,0:29:44.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,真是 乙檀大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.28,0:29:47.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,沒錯 是我 不是做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.95,0:29:50.15,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.62,0:29:56.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 什麼都不要問
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.13,0:30:00.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這個孩子 這個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.16,0:30:03.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我得先叫醫員
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.37,0:30:04.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.30,0:30:08.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,馬上會有人追過來
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.14,0:30:14.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 這個孩子 這個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.74,0:30:18.05,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,追過來 誰會追過來
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.05,0:30:20.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 求您了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.86,0:30:33.10,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,好 我知道了\N先從這兒出去吧 把孩子給我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.83,0:30:37.50,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 我的女兒 這個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.87,0:30:43.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,以後是要給主上殿下獻上白瓷的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.74,0:30:50.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,好吧 孩子給我 你也起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.71,0:30:52.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,跟我約定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.55,0:31:00.62,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如果我出了什麼事情\N就一定會守護這個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.62,0:31:02.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,向我保證吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.09,0:31:05.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我保證 所以快起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.87,0:31:18.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,來 來
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.88,0:31:30.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,蓮玉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.29,0:31:34.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,蓮玉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.58,0:31:55.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,蓮玉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.04,0:31:57.15,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,蓮玉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.61,0:32:00.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,孩子我會...蓮玉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.00,0:32:22.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.57,0:32:27.98,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,為父為毓道你付出了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.08,0:32:34.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你一定要成長為朝鮮最頂級的沙器匠
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.29,0:32:43.76,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,吃得真香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.70,0:32:48.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哎喲 瞧瞧 瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.04,0:32:55.50,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,蓮玉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.50,0:32:57.71,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你在看著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.44,0:33:00.64,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這個孩子是你的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.64,0:33:03.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不 是我的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.05,0:33:10.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我也曾夢想著\N能有個將白瓷獻給主上殿下的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.92,0:33:12.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我一定會
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.75,0:33:17.16,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,將這個孩子培養成\N朝鮮第一個女沙器匠
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.16,0:33:19.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你好好看著
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.46,0:33:24.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我真心 與你約定
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.34,0:33:28.54,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哎喲 瞧瞧 瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.64,0:33:32.21,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,孩子他爹 你先看會兒孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.25,0:33:37.71,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哎呦 真是可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.71,0:33:38.81,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.81,0:33:39.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.05,0:33:47.62,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哎喲 你餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.99,0:33:49.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.09,0:33:52.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,來 喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.96,0:33:57.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就這樣 就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.27,0:34:00.10,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哎 當什麼沙器匠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.10,0:34:01.94,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我可不願意
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.00,0:34:30.57,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,幹嘛總是要做這種東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.57,0:34:33.50,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,甭管是誰做的\N到臨了反正都要給砸碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.50,0:34:36.07,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,到時候不還是再填填補補拿去賣了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.07,0:34:36.81,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.81,0:34:38.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,填補什麼 誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.27,0:34:40.48,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,因為看著好端端的碗漏水
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.48,0:34:43.05,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,酒家的大叔可沒少發脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.05,0:34:43.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,漏水
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.78,0:34:45.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,漏水嗎 真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.98,0:34:48.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,啊 怎麼會漏水呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.92,0:34:50.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,火靈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.02,0:34:51.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你沒告訴我爹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.85,0:34:53.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我爹還不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.32,0:34:56.63,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,說是你賣出去多少碗就送出去三倍的數
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.63,0:34:59.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,老師好言相勸把人打發走了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.03,0:35:02.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井兒
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.87,0:35:03.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.97,0:35:05.43,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.54,0:35:08.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.68,0:35:23.79,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那在幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.79,0:35:25.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我在做陶瓷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.19,0:35:29.66,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,轉過身來
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.03,0:35:33.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,轉過身來
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.80,0:35:37.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哇 是箭哎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.07,0:35:46.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,慢慢地拉弓
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.74,0:35:49.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.85,0:35:51.31,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,得看著靶子
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.31,0:35:54.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,下巴尖 下臉頰 還有脖子這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.25,0:35:55.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,收攏雙肩
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.35,0:35:58.29,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,啊 到底什麼時候才射啦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.29,0:36:00.12,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,屏住呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.12,0:36:00.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,現在
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.86,0:36:03.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,現在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.73,0:36:08.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我不幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.56,0:36:10.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,還是刀更快
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.13,0:36:11.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,快給我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.87,0:36:13.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井兒 很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.34,0:36:16.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我是朝鮮最棒的劍客柳井
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.27,0:36:17.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,會傷著的 井兒
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.74,0:36:18.84,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井兒
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.21,0:36:21.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井兒 會傷著啦
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.75,0:36:30.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井兒 很危險的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.86,0:36:41.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井兒
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.80,0:36:45.63,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井兒 沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.63,0:36:47.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井兒
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.77,0:36:52.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,來了啊 爹
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.61,0:36:56.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,火靈啊 帶著你爹先去房裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.65,0:36:58.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.85,0:36:59.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.95,0:37:02.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我都吩咐過讓你悠著點 會有貴客來訪
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.89,0:37:05.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你到底怎麼聽我這當爹的話的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.92,0:37:08.76,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,把這裏收拾乾淨了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.76,0:37:10.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,乖乖地待在你房裏
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.96,0:37:12.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.83,0:37:19.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,當然是跟朝鮮最棒的沙器匠學了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.77,0:37:21.24,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,還有同門陪伴
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.24,0:37:24.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,所以說我這當爹的心裏多踏實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.91,0:37:26.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 爹
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.01,0:37:30.41,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,跟老師學習不知是何等的樂事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.51,0:37:32.98,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,只不過
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.08,0:37:35.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,只不過什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.02,0:37:38.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,說說看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.69,0:37:44.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,沒有可競爭的同門 略感可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.20,0:37:50.23,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你的意思是說\N我們井兒不是你的同門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.23,0:37:53.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井兒是這世上誰都無法取代的摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.90,0:37:57.94,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可是 她意不在陶瓷
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.94,0:38:00.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,所以才覺得不是可競爭的同門
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.14,0:38:01.24,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,火靈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.55,0:38:06.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,此話倒是不假
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.75,0:38:08.22,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,得有競爭對像
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.22,0:38:10.79,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,實力才有長進
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.52,0:38:14.46,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我能走到邊首這個位置
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.46,0:38:18.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,也是因為有摯友和競爭對手的存在\N才能成為可能
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.49,0:38:19.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你說的是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.96,0:38:21.43,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,李江天
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.43,0:38:24.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就是分院郎廳
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.83,0:38:27.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,火靈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.30,0:38:29.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你出去 拿點米酒過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.87,0:38:31.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.54,0:38:34.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.78,0:38:43.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,李江天是位摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.45,0:38:46.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你當真如此想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.39,0:38:49.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,當我深陷謀反罪之時 救我於水火的人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.32,0:38:51.16,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,便是江天
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.16,0:38:53.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,自你離開之後
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.00,0:38:54.83,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,詭異的傳聞一直不斷
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.83,0:38:55.56,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.67,0:38:59.60,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,光海君大人可還好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.60,0:39:01.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你這人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.17,0:39:04.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你這對世間萬象不感興趣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.01,0:39:06.94,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎麼就每次都如此關心大人的消息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.94,0:39:09.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,多虧大人的誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.14,0:39:12.08,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我才免於處斬 僥倖獲得一命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.81,0:39:15.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,雖然未得見
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.02,0:39:16.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,但畢竟是我的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.85,0:39:18.69,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我一直是如此想的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.14,0:39:39.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.98,0:39:41.08,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.08,0:39:42.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,光海君大人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.25,0:39:52.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您找我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.09,0:39:53.56,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,在出發開始狩獵之前
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.56,0:39:55.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我有話要對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.02,0:39:56.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,定當銘記於心
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.49,0:39:57.59,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,第一
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.59,0:40:00.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不能跑在 我這個長子的前面
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.90,0:40:02.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.00,0:40:03.10,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,理應如此
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.10,0:40:04.93,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,另外此次狩獵
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.93,0:40:07.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你不可捕獲任何的獵物
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.14,0:40:08.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.44,0:40:11.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,為何不作答
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.91,0:40:14.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,既已來狩獵
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.11,0:40:15.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,當然就要狩獵了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.58,0:40:17.05,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.41,0:40:19.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你現在是要違抗我的意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.25,0:40:21.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我只是要狩獵
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.45,0:40:22.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,斷不是要贏過兄長的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.92,0:40:24.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您大可放心
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.39,0:40:27.69,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你要再三銘記在心
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.34,0:40:50.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.18,0:40:52.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你為何要阻攔
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.28,0:40:55.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那頭鹿不是父王殿下的獵物嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.95,0:40:58.52,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,若是想要在此次狩獵中\N展現兄長的氣量
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.52,0:41:00.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就要瞄準其他的獵物
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.36,0:41:02.56,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要走哪邊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.29,0:41:04.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.39,0:41:06.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,深山處會有很多野獸的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.33,0:41:08.43,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.43,0:41:09.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您請先吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.53,0:41:11.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不了 你來開路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.10,0:41:13.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.68,0:41:26.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你又要去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.78,0:41:29.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哦 額...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.35,0:41:32.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,啊 去採集白土
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.65,0:41:34.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可真是奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.49,0:41:38.16,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我剛剛去酒家\N泰道哥哥說你要去狩獵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.16,0:41:40.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.00,0:41:42.56,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,此事我可不知
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.93,0:41:45.50,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要在日落之前回來 我得趕緊走了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.87,0:41:47.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.11,0:42:33.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我不是早吩咐你不要狩獵
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.95,0:42:36.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,-為何不等我\N-趕緊去抓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.89,0:42:40.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,已經中箭了 相信逃不了多遠
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.29,0:42:42.76,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你今日墜馬
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.76,0:42:44.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怕死狩不了獵了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.80,0:42:47.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.90,0:42:49.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.46,0:43:21.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什麼呀 這是
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.66,0:43:23.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,到底是誰跟這兒挖的陷阱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.94,0:44:02.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,陷阱逮到什麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.51,0:44:04.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,野豬
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.71,0:44:07.54,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,蟒蛇 鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.64,0:44:10.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,陷阱是我提議挖的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.85,0:44:13.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,所以那裏面的獵物都歸我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.42,0:44:14.88,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,知道了吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.88,0:44:17.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你只是動動嘴皮子\N真正辛苦挖掘的可是我耶
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.19,0:44:20.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小氣鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.39,0:44:23.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你辛苦的時候 我又沒閒著
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.33,0:44:24.79,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我也...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.98,0:44:45.71,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.71,0:44:47.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我去逮住那隻鹿再去
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.92,0:44:50.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,好 不過陷阱裏面的獵物都歸我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.85,0:44:52.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不許反悔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.69,0:44:54.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,以防萬一 來 拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.86,0:45:02.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.70,0:45:05.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,看來逮到了一隻大的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.00,0:45:09.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,難道是...老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.68,0:45:22.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.52,0:45:24.62,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.37,0:45:38.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你為何只顧著看
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.20,0:45:40.04,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,還不快把我弄出這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.77,0:45:42.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,原來不是獵物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.97,0:45:44.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.81,0:45:45.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,獵物
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.28,0:45:49.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,難道這陷阱是你挖的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.95,0:45:52.88,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,對 我就是這陷阱的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.88,0:45:55.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,幹嘛未經允許就擅自鑽進去呀
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.55,0:45:59.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,等我上去 絕不饒你
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.86,0:46:01.69,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那請試著上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.99,0:46:06.83,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我...我說
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.93,0:46:09.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.40,0:46:11.60,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,起碼得弄我出去再走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.97,0:46:13.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,還不快給我回來
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.45,0:46:27.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,看您這上來會跟我拚命的架勢\N我幹嘛要救您吶
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.75,0:46:29.59,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你可知道我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.95,0:46:33.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你若棄我不顧 一定會招來滅門之禍
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.72,0:46:36.56,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,真是有夠煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.93,0:46:39.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您就省點力氣 安靜呆著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.06,0:46:43.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,胳膊被蛇咬了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.00,0:46:48.67,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,若不趕快治療 毒會擴散到全身的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.67,0:46:50.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.61,0:46:53.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.81,0:46:54.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.38,0:46:57.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.40,0:47:19.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你這人真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.87,0:47:21.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,連我都陷進來怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.70,0:47:22.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎麼出去呀
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.80,0:47:24.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,跪下
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.37,0:47:26.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.11,0:47:27.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我叫你跪下
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.58,0:47:29.41,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,還是你跪下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.41,0:47:31.98,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那麼等我出去之後會放繩子下來
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.98,0:47:33.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,叫我如何相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.82,0:47:37.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我會出去喊軍隊來 跪下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.22,0:47:40.79,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如此深山老林 還什麼軍隊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.79,0:47:44.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,看來您中毒不輕啊 滿嘴胡言亂語
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.83,0:47:48.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哪條胳膊啊 得先處理蛇毒了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.53,0:47:54.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您撒謊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.10,0:47:58.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,為了騙我 撒謊說被蛇咬傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.14,0:48:00.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.71,0:48:02.81,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是這條胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.35,0:48:14.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這...這可怎麼辦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.92,0:48:17.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這毒都擴散到肩膀了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.13,0:48:18.23,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.43,0:48:24.10,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,看來 只好砍掉手臂了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.47,0:48:27.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你這是在戲弄我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.77,0:48:29.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什麼戲弄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.61,0:48:31.81,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,都沒被咬 怎麼可能擴散...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.38,0:48:39.88,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,張口就撒謊 所以才會踩到\N這只有野獸才會踩的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.25,0:48:42.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大膽 你可知道我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.45,0:48:45.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,竟敢拿野獸與我相提並論
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.12,0:48:47.22,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我乃
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.99,0:48:55.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我乃本國的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.50,0:49:00.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您真的是王子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.44,0:49:04.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,正是 還不快給我跪下
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.57,0:49:08.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 小的罪該萬死
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.14,0:49:10.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,請您饒小的一命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.35,0:49:13.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小的太過低賤 沒能認出尊貴的您
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.65,0:49:16.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,罷了 不知者無罪 我寬宏...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.95,0:49:19.15,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你以為我會這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.89,0:49:23.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,跟你說敬語 都覺得可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.19,0:49:23.93,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.93,0:49:26.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,王子 真可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.86,0:49:28.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你騙過多少人了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.70,0:49:30.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你就不怕遭天譴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.53,0:49:32.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,閉嘴 臭丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.00,0:49:32.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.30,0:49:38.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你給我聽好嘍 我哥哥就快來了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.97,0:49:44.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,若再敢撒謊\N我就叫哥哥只救我 把你撇在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.11,0:49:45.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.68,0:49:49.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,很好 到時候一定會被滅三族
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.25,0:49:51.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你就試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.09,0:49:52.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哎呦 好害怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.92,0:49:55.12,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你以為嚇我 我就不敢了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.23,0:49:59.16,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哥哥 快來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.90,0:50:01.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這裏一個奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.73,0:50:04.67,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哥哥 泰道哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.70,0:51:07.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.57,0:51:14.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這是我的獵物
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.40,0:51:15.50,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,退下
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.50,0:51:18.07,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這確實是我的箭 您為何這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.44,0:51:22.48,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙 看不到肚子上的箭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.85,0:51:25.05,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這不是沒射中要害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.05,0:51:28.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是被我射中腦袋死的\N所以這只野豬是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.45,0:51:30.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙竟敢...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.92,0:51:36.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,再加上這支箭與您的箭不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.53,0:51:41.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您看 與您的顏色完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.93,0:51:45.23,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,還愣著做什麼 還不給我綁了這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.23,0:51:46.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.74,0:51:54.41,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,放開我 我到底做錯了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.15,0:52:09.83,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你說的哥哥呢 到底甚麼時候來
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.66,0:52:13.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你確定他會來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.86,0:52:16.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你確定有哥哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.43,0:52:17.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,都說會來了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.63,0:52:23.04,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,一定是打了條大獵物 來得慢罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.41,0:52:24.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.97,0:52:29.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那我出去找你哥哥來 跪下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.28,0:52:32.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你又沒見過他 怎麼找
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.95,0:52:35.88,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就算出去 也得是我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.88,0:52:38.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,該跪下的人是你
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.19,0:52:40.66,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我不是說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.66,0:52:42.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我可是一國王子
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.33,0:52:47.26,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是不能跪下的身子
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.63,0:52:50.93,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,世上哪有不能跪下的身體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.93,0:52:54.60,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,兩條胳膊往前伸 膝蓋像這樣跪著
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.60,0:52:55.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.61,0:53:07.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,滾開 你這無禮之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.39,0:53:11.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,無禮之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.49,0:53:13.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,對呀 你說對了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.32,0:53:15.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,所以別跟我這種無禮之徒待在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.89,0:53:17.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,快把我弄出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.73,0:53:20.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你不是還有哥哥來找你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.03,0:53:23.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,看來你想逃跑 這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.97,0:53:27.64,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,等從這裏出去 就押你去官衙\N等著瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.64,0:53:28.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,官衙
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.84,0:53:32.04,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你真是自掘墳墓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.04,0:53:35.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這可是你說的 到時候可別怨我
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.34,0:53:38.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這是我要說的話 還是擔心你自個兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.68,0:53:44.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哥哥怎麼還不賴
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.36,0:53:48.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,出了什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.74,0:54:11.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你這個小偷 你這還算是男人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.68,0:54:13.52,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你這一生都得偷下去
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.62,0:54:15.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.16,0:54:26.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.36,0:54:31.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,一箭未射卻奪人獵物\N怎麼能算得上是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.60,0:54:38.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,一箭未射 你很好奇我的射術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.94,0:54:42.88,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,好 我就親自射給你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.91,0:55:17.38,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.19,0:55:27.66,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那孩子是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.49,0:55:30.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,琿兒去哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.96,0:55:35.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,啊 那個 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.00,0:55:36.10,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,帶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.10,0:55:36.83,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.91,0:55:48.21,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,還不趕緊跪下 這位是主上殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.31,0:55:51.15,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,放肆 你這混帳
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.55,0:55:58.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,因為看不到琿兒 所以我一直在找
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.49,0:56:02.16,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,但是這傢伙\N帶著插有琿兒箭矢的獵物出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.16,0:56:03.63,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,琿兒的箭矢
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.63,0:56:05.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 父王
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.09,0:56:10.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,此人舉止古怪 怕是否加害於琿兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.97,0:56:13.17,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,所以我正在進行審問
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.17,0:56:14.64,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你加害於他了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.74,0:56:19.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不 我根本就不知道他是誰\N也沒見過他
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.78,0:56:21.24,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我只是把那只受傷的野豬...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.24,0:56:26.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,父王 我將繼續審問 查出琿兒的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.75,0:56:28.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,請您允許
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.36,0:56:35.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,老闆 我們的湯飯怎麼還不送上來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.19,0:56:37.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,-稍微等一下嘛...\N-來了 馬上就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.76,0:56:39.60,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,金泰道的父親是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.33,0:56:43.63,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是我啊 出什麼事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.63,0:56:45.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,馬上把這傢伙抓起來
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.47,0:56:46.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.20,0:56:50.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,-為什麼啊...\N-大人 為什麼抓人啊... -老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.35,0:57:03.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,泰道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.45,0:57:04.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,-爹\N-泰道
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.92,0:57:05.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,泰道
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.76,0:57:07.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,爹
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.59,0:57:11.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,到底是何罪名 竟然連我爹也抓來了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.53,0:57:13.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我們是無辜的 我們冤枉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.00,0:57:16.67,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,閉上嘴 安靜地等候殿下的發落吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.03,0:57:19.23,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.23,0:57:22.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哎呦 這可真是晴天霹靂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.64,0:57:26.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井兒呢 逃走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.31,0:57:29.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我說 請幫我叫大人過來
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.81,0:57:39.05,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我們仔細搜查了酒肆\N當光海君大人並不再那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.05,0:57:41.62,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你這也算報告嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.62,0:57:45.66,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要是不能馬上找回來\N我就要砍了兼司僕將你的腦袋
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.66,0:57:46.76,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.76,0:57:52.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,父王 我要通過那傢伙把琿兒找回來
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.94,0:57:58.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你不是不知道他是誰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.51,0:58:01.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,雖然我不認識大人\N但我對這座山瞭如指掌
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.44,0:58:05.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如果我能在天黑前找到大人\N那就請您放了我和我爹
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.11,0:58:11.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,好 不過如果找不到\N我就要對你實施懲罰了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.14,0:58:31.54,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哥哥做得挺好啊 我怎麼就不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.54,0:58:34.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎麼這麼冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.11,0:58:36.31,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你以為我生火是因為閒得沒事幹麼
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.31,0:58:39.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這裏可是大夏天也會結冰的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.25,0:58:41.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那就趕緊生火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.29,0:58:45.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你要是行 你就試試啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.88,0:59:09.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.45,0:59:12.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你打算凍死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.65,0:59:17.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這可是之前在森林裏迷路時\N救了我哥和我性命的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.52,0:59:22.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,常言道 男女七歲不同席\N你這是何古怪之舉
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.19,0:59:25.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你這無禮的傢伙\N還想顧及自己的體面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.23,0:59:29.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,俗話說 好死不如賴活著
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.90,0:59:32.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要是不想被凍死就老實地待著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.25,0:59:51.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.65,0:59:55.59,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我只是按照你說的做而已
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.59,0:59:57.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,呃...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.26,1:00:32.29,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可以感受到溫熱 看來可以撐下去了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.40,1:00:35.60,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你往那邊點
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.60,1:00:40.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,幹嘛啊 我可不想被凍死呢
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.44,1:00:51.38,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,混賬 你都對我做了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.11,1:00:54.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你到底做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.32,1:00:59.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我又沒跑步 心臟為何跳得這麼快啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.13,1:01:04.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你笑什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.53,1:01:10.10,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,別光顧著笑 趕緊回答我
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.24,1:01:21.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那是因為你被我迷住了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.95,1:01:29.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,迷住 我被你迷住嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.35,1:01:57.81,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.81,1:01:59.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 您在哪兒啊...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.28,1:02:00.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,琿兒...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.75,1:02:02.22,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 您在哪兒啊...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.22,1:02:03.69,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.26,1:02:07.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.72,1:02:09.56,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,終於來了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.93,1:02:12.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,聽那一陣馬蹄聲\N肯定是我的軍士們來了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.86,1:02:16.17,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你看 我說過他們肯定會來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.00,1:02:21.67,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 難道說...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.14,1:02:30.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你真的是大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.67,1:02:52.13,Next2,,0,0,0,,*下集預告*
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.13,1:02:56.54,Next2,,0,0,0,,萬一一是百姓對王子大人大聲咒罵\N還動手打他
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.54,1:02:58.01,Next2,,0,0,0,,那會怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.01,1:02:59.47,Next2,,0,0,0,,我要馬上對你處斬
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.47,1:03:02.04,Next2,,0,0,0,,您說忘情定要找到一個人見到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.04,1:03:04.61,Next2,,0,0,0,,木劍對真劍可不合適
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.61,1:03:05.71,Next2,,0,0,0,,我不想再見到您了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.71,1:03:07.18,Next2,,0,0,0,,你倒是抗辯一下啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.18,1:03:08.28,Next2,,0,0,0,,我怕再見面時又會失去什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.28,1:03:10.49,Next2,,0,0,0,,將光海任命為分院的副提調
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.49,1:03:12.69,Next2,,0,0,0,,萬萬不可啊 殿下
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.69,1:03:14.52,Next2,,0,0,0,,製造一個豐饒祭上使用祭器吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.52,1:03:16.73,Next2,,0,0,0,,我將奉御命製造祭器
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.73,1:03:21.13,Next2,,0,0,0,,只要我還是朗廳 你就休想涉足分院
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.13,1:03:23.33,Next2,,0,0,0,,您是誰 為何如此胡言亂語
